-- Germany Sees Its Financial Risks Growing With IMF’s EU Role: FTD
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2011-12-15T21:56:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-15/germany-sees-its-financial-risks-growing-with-imf-s-eu-role-ftd.html
Germany ’s central bank expects any
bigger involvement by the  International Monetary Fund  in trying
to resolve  Europe ’s debt crisis to increase the risk of
financial losses for Germany, as its participation would also be
enlarged,  Financial Times Deutschland  reported in a preview of
an article that will be published tomorrow, citing unnamed
people at the Bundesbank.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
